{"tid":919330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載] 正式成立「拯救廚師腸大聯盟」去信代理商！","createTime":"2018-11-28T03:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T03:34:25.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7cc87a6b0c8aa2e6bf414f7253d1118f8ac9e21","tid":919330,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"「拯救瀕危廚房腸 港人唔係得個樣」<br />\n明日，本組將去信廚師腸香港代理商，要求保證1月後仍有廚師腸對港供貨，本組現嚴正呼籲各大議員，為市民福祉，請立即採取行動。表達對港人頹飯福利之關注。本組現正收集聯署，要求在美游說獨立關稅區之議員與官員對Valley Chef提出嚴正交涉，要求停止執行破產保護。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本組亦會去信不同商業機構，提出收購可能，確保港人有穩定之廚師腸供貨。<br />\n<br />\n本組向廚師腸愛好者發出嚴正呼籲，要人為己，不要屯積居奇，分享才是美德！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/212106159682477/posts/212115593014867/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F212106159682477%2Fposts%2F212115593014867%2F&d=uNoWp92JVkE6MadDRBf1ONU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6f1c9035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/212106159682477/posts/212115593014867/</a><br />\n<br />\nfrom 飲食台<br />\n正式成立「拯救廚師腸大聯盟」去信代理商！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/917689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/917689</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a9c049e56ee04fcb4042691550c7b77b57764e","tid":919330,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"停止執行破產保護 = 唔會破產？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8a9835525c0dfa79771ede1557b02d2c7e47fc","tid":919330,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22a9c049e56ee04fcb4042691550c7b77b57764e","tid":919330,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"停止執行破產保護 = 唔會破產？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"唔撚理<br />\n總